titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER to SHOW CAUSE signed by Magistrate Judge Gregory G. Hollows on 1/19/12. titleInfo.subTitle: ORDER signed by Magistrate Judge Gregory G. Hollows on 8/23/12 ORDERING that Plaintiff's MOTION for Summary Judgment 19 is GRANTED in part pursuant to Sentence Four of 42 U.S.C. ยง 405(g). The Commissioner's Cross-MOTION For Summary Judgment 24 is DENIED, and this matter is REMANDED for further findings in accordance with this order. The Clerk is directed to enter Judgment for Plaintiff. Given the satisfactory showing made in the Declaration of Bess M. Brewer 18, the 1/20/12 order to show cause why this case should not be dismissed for lack of prosecution is DISCHARGED. CASE CLOSED. (Mena-Sanchez, L)
